OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FEurope is currently the world leader
OL,7,Fin particle physics ` but China has
OL,8,Fplans for a bigger and more powerful
OL,9,Fgiant collider. ITV News Science
OL,10,FCorrespondent Martin Stew reports
OL,12,FWords by ITV News Health and Science
OL,13,FProducer Rhiannon Hopley
OL,15,FBeneath the mountains at the Swiss-
OL,16,FFrench border, as deep as 175 metres
OL,17,Fbelow ground, lies the Large Hadron
OL,18,FCollider ` the world's biggest and
OL,19,Fmost powerful particle accelerator.
