OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FIt's a 27-kilometre ring where beams
OL,7,Fof particles are fired at each other
OL,8,Fat nearly the speed of the light.
OL,10,FWhen they collide, they break up into
OL,11,Fsmaller particles that scientists
OL,12,Fanalyse in the hope of making new
OL,13,Fdiscoveries about how the universe
OL,14,Fworks ` including what happened just
OL,15,Fafter the Big Bang.
OL,17,FIt's the largest physics experiment in
OL,18,Fthe world, but scientists want to make
OL,19,Fit even bigger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
