OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FThey want to build the Future Circular
OL,7,FCollider ` it would be more than three
OL,8,Ftimes longer than the current tunnel
OL,9,Fat 91 kilometres.
OL,11,FEurope is currently the world leader
OL,12,Fin particle physics ` but China is
OL,13,Fsnapping at its heels with its own
OL,14,Fplans for a an even bigger and more
OL,15,Fpowerful giant collider called the
OL,16,FCircular Electron Positron Collider.
OL,18,FIt would be just as big as the
OL,19,Fproposed new European collider and
OL,20,Fwould challenge European supremacy in
OL,21,Fparticle physics.
