OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FIt could begin building as early as
OL,7,F2027.
OL,9,FThe new director general in waiting of
OL,10,FCERN is British scientist Professor
OL,11,FMark Thomson. He will take over
OL,12,Fofficially in January 2026.
OL,14,FOne of his biggest tasks will be
OL,15,Fconvincing European governments to
OL,16,Ffund the new collider at CERN at a
OL,17,Fcost of #13 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
