OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,F"This is spread over 15 years not a
OL,7,Fone-off spend, and it is shared
OL,8,Fbetween 24 member states of CERN and
OL,9,Fother international partners,"
OL,10,FProfessor Thompson said.
OL,12,F"To convince the government there are
OL,13,Fmany arguments. One is the science,
OL,14,Fand you have to base why you're doing
OL,15,Fit on the science. Then there is the
OL,16,Fwider economic impact of working right
OL,17,Fat the forefront of science and
OL,18,Ftechnology which will then filter down
OL,19,Finto the economy," he added.
