OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FThe Large Hadron Collider (LHC) is
OL,7,Fcurrently in shutdown for maintenance
OL,8,Fand the High Luminosity upgrade.
OL,10,FThis will increase the brightness of
OL,11,Fthe collisions by ten times, meaning
OL,12,Fthere will also be ten times more data.
OL,14,FHowever, after this upgrade, the LHC
OL,15,Fwill be nearing its limit on how much
OL,16,Ffurther the science can be pushed with
OL,17,Fthe current equipment.
OL,19,FProfessor Thompson said the new
OL,20,Fcollider will be necessary in order to
OL,21,Fcontinue groundbreaking research.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
