OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FIf China build its large collider and
OL,7,FEurope does not, there is a risk that
OL,8,Ftalent will also be lost as scientists
OL,9,Fgo to work in Asia instead.
OL,11,F"I think there's an argument that we
OL,12,Freally have to stay at that forefront
OL,13,Fbecause it really is one of the few,
OL,14,Fvery few areas where we have the lead
OL,15,Fin Europe compared to other parts of
OL,16,Fthe world," he said.
OL,18,FAt the end of March, CERN released a
OL,19,F"feasibility report" outlining how
OL,20,Fthis project would work and the
OL,21,Fpracticality of its construction.
